00:39:37.250 --> 00:39:40.580
What you don&#39;t want is a
blow-up with a bunch of, you

00:39:40.580 --> 00:39:42.800
know, debts that the company
owe, and everyone, you know,

00:39:42.800 --> 00:39:44.950
showing up to work, one day,
and the door being locked.

00:39:46.830 --> 00:39:47.760
You&#39;ll know when you&#39;re
failing,

00:39:47.760 --> 00:39:48.890
you&#39;ll know when the company
is,

00:39:48.890 --> 00:39:50.450
things just aren&#39;t going to
work,

00:39:50.450 --> 00:39:52.500
and you should just tell your
investors.

00:39:52.500 --> 00:39:54.230
Like, hey, sorry, this isn&#39;t
going to work.

00:39:54.230 --> 00:39:55.310
No one will be surprised.

00:39:55.310 --> 00:39:58.330
Like, I expect to lose my, or
I&#39;m willing to lose my money

00:39:58.330 --> 00:40:00.120
on every investment I ever
make.

00:40:00.120 --> 00:40:01.590
I know that happens most of
the time, and

00:40:01.590 --> 00:40:02.540
the winners pay for it,

00:40:02.540 --> 00:40:04.240
you know, still with a factor
of 100, so it&#39;s okay.

00:40:05.950 --> 00:40:09.660
No one, people will be very
understanding and supportive.

00:40:09.660 --> 00:40:11.530
But you want to tell people
early.

00:40:11.530 --> 00:40:13.020
You don&#39;t want to surprise
them.

